## Common Examples

```tsx
// ✅ Correct conversions
<div className="w-3 h-3">     // 24px icons
<div className="w-4 h-4">     // 32px icons
<div className="p-2">         // 16px padding
<div className="gap-3">       // 24px gap
<div className="m-4">         // 32px margin

// ❌ Common mistakes (using default Tailwind assumptions)
<div className="w-6 h-6">     // This is 40px, NOT 24px!
<div className="p-4">         // This is 32px, NOT 16px!
<div className="gap-6">       // This is 40px, NOT 24px!
```

## Workflow

1. Extract pixel value from Figma
2. Look up in table above
3. Use corresponding Tailwind class
4. Verify in browser DevTools

